dct_title_s: New York Bay Bulkhead and Pierhead
dct_description_sm: Map shows the bulkhead area granted, bulkhead area states lands, pierhead area granted, pierhead area states land, and United States pierhead area. Map shows which lands were granted or leased and which were not. Bedloes Island, Ellis Island, Staten Island, Jersey City, and Bayonne shown.
